text: Dmitriyevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Dmitriyevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 224 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Zilair. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Dmitriyevka, Zilairsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
